data.description: Presenting this fabulous 2-bedroom residence nestled on a PRIME corner lot backing up to expansive green space! Interior features a formal living room w/tile flooring throughout & abundant natural light. Sliding glass doors open to the back patio from the spacious great room, merging the indoor experience w/the outdoors. The lovely kitchen has recessed lighting, a pantry, ample cabinet space, built-in appliances, travertine backsplash, granite counters, & a prep island w/a breakfast bar. Adding to the home's functionality is a den with double doors, ideal for an office/bedroom. A private ensuite w/dual sinks & a walk-in closet complete this large main retreat.
